    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Brand name of a floor or grounds covering made of vinyl and nylon made to resemble turf. Used primarily on athletic playing fields and on outdoor patios.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
